                <div class="col-12 m-0 p-0 d-flex justify-content-center"><span style="font-size:14px; font-weight:500;">여러 납품형태를 갖추고 있으며,</span></div>
                <div class="col-12 m-0 p-0 d-flex justify-content-center"><span style="font-size:14px; font-weight:500;">직제조 과정으로 합리적인 가격입니다.</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-3 row d-flex justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-12 m-0 p-0 d-flex justify-content-center"><img src="https://cdn.imweb.me/thumbnail/20220215/970fe2667ce30.png" style="height:250px;" /></div>
                <div class="col-12 p-0 d-flex justify-content-center" style="margin:0; margin-top: 20px;"><span style="font-size:25px; font-weight:900;">합리적인 공급을 위한</span></div>
                <div class="col-12 m-0 p-0 d-flex justify-content-center"><span style="font-size:25px; font-weight:900;">자체 제조, 물류시설 운영</span></div>
                <div class="col-12 p-0 d-flex justify-content-center" style="margin:0; margin-top:10px;"><span style="font-size:14px; font-weight:500;">직경매ㆍ직수입의 안정적인 물류 인프라로</span></div>
                <div class="col-12 m-0 p-0 d-flex justify-content-center"><span style="font-size:14px; font-weight:500;">어떠한 시장상황에서도 안정적인</span></div>
                <div class="col-12 m-0 p-0 d-flex justify-content-center"><span style="font-size:14px; font-weight:500;">물류 확보 및 원활한 수급이 가능합니다.</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-3 row d-flex justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-12 m-0 p-0 d-flex justify-content-center"><img src="https://cdn.imweb.me/thumbnail/20220901/115ca35890eb4.png" style="height:250px;" /></div>
                <div class="col-12 p-0 d-flex justify-content-center" style="margin:0; margin-top: 20px;"><span style="font-size:25px; font-weight:900;">까다롭게 관리하는</span></div>
                <div class="col-12 m-0 p-0 d-flex justify-content-center"><span style="font-size:25px; font-weight:900;">철저한 위생시스템</span></div>
                <div class="col-12 p-0 d-flex justify-content-center" style="margin:0; margin-top:10px;"><span style="font-size:14px; font-weight:500;">HACCP 인증을 받은</span></div>
                <div class="col-12 m-0 p-0 d-flex justify-content-center"><span style="font-size:14px; font-weight:500;">깨끗하고안전한 제조시설에서</span></div>
                <div class="col-12 m-0 p-0 d-flex justify-content-center"><span style="font-size:14px; font-weight:500;">위생적인 식품을 생산하고 있습니다.</span></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 row m-0 p-0 d-flex justify-content-center">
            <button type="button" class="OMD_btn" style="">OME/ODM 자세히 알아보기</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
